Now open any .tex file and press Ctrl+Alt+b to build 
(or use VSCode Command Palette to run command LaTeX Workshop: Build with Recipe). 
From the options that pop up, select latexmk recipe.

Press Ctrl+Alt+v to view generated PDF file 
(select the Preview Inside VSCode option to open it side-by-side with the editor). 
Edit the .tex file to see changes reflected in PDF in real time.